      "identifier": "ea:concept:ai-agent",
      "name": "AI Agent",
      "abstract": "AI agents combine models, tools, memory, environmental feedback, stopping conditions, permissions and evaluation in an iterative action loop.",
      "description": "An AI agent is a software system in which a model can select actions, use tools, observe results and adapt its next steps toward an objective within defined boundaries.",
